reviewText: Fast delivery, and the movie was awesome ridiculously funny..
I use this video in my high school Spanish classes.  The kids can follow the story even though they don't understand all of the dialogue and I get a kick out of the double meanings.  Win-win!

This DVD arrived as described. The cartoon is funny, but you must be able to understand alot of slang and sarcasm used in the Mexican community. Not all Spanish speaking people use the same words or terms in the same way. The cartoon is extremely funny for adults.
